b market for both the formally educated population and the marginalised groups\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Re-inventing the life wealth cycle for the communities who have long depended on day by day, hand to mouth living. Depriving the generational lineage of exposure or hopes for a better life.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating an environment of empowered societies that can then have the capacity for sustainable consumption, renewable energy, circular economies and all other major initiatives that we need collaborated for our \u201cworld\u201d to survive.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasten the process of inclusion for the marginalised groups and genders, and pivoting their equality. If they are financially self-empowered, there it would be hard if not impossible to ignore their opinions and how society would view them or\u00a0 impose on them<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Speeding up the development of rural towns and inter-trade. Not to mention expansion of current SMEs into new territories, through digital skills and access.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><b>How we do this, is through :<\/b><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coursework access from International and National institutions of digital learning<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">E.U and developing cooperation partner support<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Business and trade beneficiaries of a more digitized Africa<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Telcos, Ecommerce sites, Construction and transportation, E-health institutions, Insurance and many others<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=&#8221;transparent&#8221; up=&#8221;40&#8243; up_style=&#8221;px&#8221; down=&#8221;0&#8243; down_style=&#8221;px&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;58270&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; qode_hover_animation=&#8221;&#8221; qode_css_animation=&#8221;element_from_left&#8221; transition_delay=&#8221;0.1&#8243;][vc_column_text]<b>How we expand our reach and enforce immediate empowerment from graduates:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We use peer and program-graduate learning as the main first assignment for the groups, where they can immediately:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Grow confidence in the marketability and value of digital\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Begin earning from the digital skills and knowledge they have acquired<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Expand inter-nation communication and networking. (Many great regionally beneficial ideas and solutions are born from this)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Widen the reach of the program and getting higher affinity from the targeted groups through being the frontrunners of the skilling program<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bringing a new dynamic to approaches during peer conversations and discussions towards problems in the community<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=&#8221;transparent&#8221; up=&#8221;20&#8243; up_style=&#8221;px&#8221; down=&#8221;0&#8243; down_style=&#8221;px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row row_type=&#8221;row&#8221; use_row_as_full_screen_section=&#8221;no&#8221; type=&#8221;grid&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;93&#8243; padding_botto